Package scalf

Contains all of the classes created by Samuel Scalf.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Shapes
    A command line-driven program that calculates the area or volume of a two-dimensional or three-dimensional shape, respectively (See scalf.package1).

Package scalf Description

Contains all of the classes created by Samuel Scalf.

The primary purpose of this package was to ensure there were no conflicts with other students' classes that may use the same names. This class was left at the "root" package level for ease of use. In other words, instead of typing "java scalf.project1.Shapes" a user can type "java scalf.Shapes"
